General Information

Olay Regenerist Micro-Exfoliating Wet Cleansing Cloths for advanced anti-aging.

What it does:

- Quickly removes dirt, oil and make-up from skin surface.

- Soap free cleansing cloth that exfoliates to remove dull, dry skin, revitalizing skin's surface.

How it works:

- Micro-textured cloths are pre-moistened with a soap-free cleanser to remove dirt, oil and make-up and gently exfoliate skin.

Boxed Contents: 30 Textured wet cloths

Size: 30 Pack

Ingredients

Water, Niacinamide (Vitamin B3), Panthenol (Pro-Vitamin B5), Ascorbic Acid (Vitamin C), Tocopheryl Acetate (Vitamin E), Hexylene Glycol, Glycerin, Dimethicone, DMDM Hydantoin, Acrylates/Vinyl Isodecanoate Crosspolymer, Polysorbate 20, Disodium EDTA, Dimethiconol, Potassium Hydroxide, Fragrance, Iodopropynyl Butylcarbamate.

Directions

Lift away dirt, make-up and dull, dry skin from around your eyes, face and neck revealing beautifully revitalized skin. Remove carton and peel label to open. Re-seal pack to keep cloths from drying out. Gently wipe face and neck clean of dirt, make-up and dull, dry skin. Dispose of used cloths in trash (do not flush).
